@startuml
title C1 — Contexto | Vista de Cenários — UC: Manage Representatives

actor "Port Authority Officer" as Officer
actor "Shipping Agent Representative" as Representative

rectangle "Port Logistics Management System (PLMS)" as PLMS {
  usecase "Create Representative" as UC_Create
  usecase "Update Representative" as UC_Update
  usecase "Deactivate Representative" as UC_Deactivate
  usecase "View Representatives" as UC_View
}

Officer --> UC_Create
Officer --> UC_Update
Officer --> UC_Deactivate
Officer --> UC_View

Representative --> UC_View

note right of UC_Create
  Officer can create new representatives 
  and assign them to existing organizations.
end note

note right of UC_Deactivate
  Deactivation prevents login but 
  preserves representative history.
end note

@enduml
